    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted based on quasi-static loading regime, literature support for rate insensitivity of Ti-6Al-4V, and the MEDIUM model risk level context. All quantitative acceptance criteria for output comparison are satisfied (E/uval < 1.96, MAPE < 10% for all QoIs). The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended regulatory use. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and has not been applied to this submission.",
